"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"在 setting 中，有一个 ENS 选项，提供把 MIRROR 中账号 ID 转换成 ENS 域名。\\n\\n![ENS in Setting](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/yVItCunuSArJzx8n7ZQPv.png?height=201&width=689)\\n\\n但是点击 Link ENS 后出现下图报错：\\n\\n![ERROR](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9_zVb0i6g6kBh09KRx_6r.png?height=76&width=314)\\n\\n进入 ENS ，在 Ropsten 网络注册 .eth 后，ENS 名称变成了 .eth 结尾短链，返回 MIRROR 仍显示不能 set。估计是需要在 Main Network 上申请才可以吧？那就不折腾了。\\n\\n注册 ENS 以及相关设置，我参考了如下链接：\\n\\n[https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/kvRCDAWl1Qr3kQFsK8B5avShMhN5ODy44OBHywdPvcY](https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/kvRCDAWl1Qr3kQFsK8B5avShMhN5ODy44OBHywdPvcY)\\n\\n不知道有谁设置好了，分享经验，学习一下。\",\"timestamp\":1641301308,\"title\":\"MIRROR 设置 ENS\"},\"digest\":\"IpgcsBfp_XmM9hXiOX-YHrtOaCoPO6Z1dfWYo12pBK0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0872437046E456BaAa75e99eDBBcC70fE3E77Bc8\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"mcB__8IWdqTuLxVnOqDf1QZ7pli-bCdjQmvpgUjqZBw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2Kt6dk6u00VORGyrOSmIGNM1LnlUyJpkaPzqfXLLU7E\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"hdklqG7atPVUzdv-uvrF9eyBoFaKsGRpvZtRBY_epY8R66Bv7VPwRWzRU0YNvRBK0IvEaOGHvtB_nnA8sHZDlQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x6a5ae9bce5cd38152691d425f8be6adf12942cf54426ca9539d2c0aee25d2d280bd3f5cb20fd208987909123189d1eeccd3baee0c57702c392acebc528652d501c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"mcB__8IWdqTuLxVnOqDf1QZ7pli-bCdjQmvpgUjqZBw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2Kt6dk6u00VORGyrOSmIGNM1LnlUyJpkaPzqfXLLU7E\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"IpgcsBfp_XmM9hXiOX-YHrtOaCoPO6Z1dfWYo12pBK0\"}"